Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初めて見た時の彼女は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まるで人形のようで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イルマの求める手紙の代筆ができるようには
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:36.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とても　見えなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:23.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イルマ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:25.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お疲れさま　アルド
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今いいかい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}紹介したい人がいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:32.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}入って
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お初にお目にかかります
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様がお望みなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どこでも駆けつけます
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形サービス
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット・エヴァーガーデンです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたがウワサのドールね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:49.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ウワサ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:55.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}郵便協会の先生がぜひあなたをって紹介してくれたのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どなたのことでしょうか?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イルマ様　ブレイディ伯爵様から花束とメッセージです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ミュンター将軍より花束とお写真です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:08.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}このあと予定されて取材の件でお話が
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アルド
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼女に明日　私の家に来るように言ってちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:15.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:19.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イルマ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あとで少し時間もらえるか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}また　あの話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:26.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もうやめましょ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨日はごめんなさいね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}さあ　そこにかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失礼します
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ねえ　ところで　昨日の私の歌は聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい　オペラを観るのは初めてでしたが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:46.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}体の奥から震わされるような歌声でした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:49.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歌詞が古典語だったため
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一部聞き取れませんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一体　何のことを歌っていたのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.36,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}仕事に移りましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}では　必要な情報を伺います
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まず　送り先の方の名前を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:19.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差出人は　イルマ・フェリーチェ様でよろしいですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私の名前じゃないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリエッタにしてちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:26.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}偽名ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まさか　違うわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして相手は彼女の恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.29,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}名前はモデスト
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦場に行って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}まだ…帰ってこないの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}モデスト様ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで名字は　住所はどちらでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなのどうでもいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大事なのは中身だから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}かしこまりました
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それでは本文のほうに移します
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よろしくお願いいたします
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい　よろしく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本文に移るのでは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから　あなたが考えてそれを書くの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦場に行ってこないモデストを想って
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恋人のマリエッタが紡ぐ恋文よ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:29.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自動手記人形
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それを書くのがあなたの仕事でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:38.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解しました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}終わりました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}読んでみて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}親愛なるモデスト様
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:04.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリエッタは現在戦闘区域外にて待機中です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}モデスト様の安否情報は確認できておりません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:13.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一刻も早くご指示をお願いします
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}マリエッタより
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:21.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何…その…軍人みたいな文章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お嬢様が私に考えろとおっしゃっていましたので
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご満足いただけてないのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その言葉を耳にした
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべての女性が共感し
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべての男性の胸を打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんな恋文が欲しいのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}共感し…胸を打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう一度書いてみて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:05.89,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}フーゴ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はあなたを永遠に慕い続けるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魂の牢獄の中でも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:27.12,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}記憶に残るあなたの甘くしびれるような声が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私を震わせ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:33.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今にも途切れそうな想いをかろうじてつなぎ止めているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いつの時代の恋文なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古すぎるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もっと今の時代のストーリーのあるものが欲しいの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:10.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたのことが愛しくて　愛しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛しくて　愛しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛しくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大げさすぎよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こんなんじゃ今どきの人は引いちゃうわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}時代をもっと感じながら書いて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:25.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}時代…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戻りました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何してんの　ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:06.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オペラ座の歌姫の恋文を代筆してるんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:11.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ものすっごいゴシップだったらこっそり教えてね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アイリス
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冗談ですって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:21.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫　何か悩みがあるじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様の…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.03,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お客様の依頼内容が
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}高度すぎるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:34.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あんたのグチなんて初めて聞いたわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:37.17,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなに難しい恋文なの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべての女性が共感し
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべての男性の胸を打つ恋文だそうです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:46.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何それ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確かに大変そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お2人にはできますか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無理ね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お疲れさま　ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アルド様　お久しぶりです
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}依頼の件　難航しているようだね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:37.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい　どんなふうに書いても満足していただきません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:42.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イルマも新作オペラにかけているからね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新作？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:47.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それが手紙と何の関係があるのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや　手紙じゃなくて歌の歌詞だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新作オペラのクライマックスで歌うアリアの…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:57.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ほら　この曲だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}え？　代筆じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歌詞を書く仕事だったってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アルド様のお話では
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最初からそういう依頼だったとのことです
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}おっかしいな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}依頼を検討する時に気づかなかったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}郵便協会から来た依頼でさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}てっきり代筆だと思い込んでたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:25.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これ　ヒロインが自分が書いた恋文を読み上げるシーンですね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なるほど　恋文には違いないってことね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:32.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで　どうするつもりなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一度受けたお仕事ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}業務内容と異なります
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんなの簡単じゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:43.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何よ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}代筆じゃなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺たちで最高の歌詞作ればいいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前なあ　そんな簡単じゃないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大丈夫だって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うちには優秀なドールがこんなにいるだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:57.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.78,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それに　実は俺だって詞を作るくらいなら…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あんたね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:09.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当にそのようなことは可能でしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}やってみなくちゃ分からねえって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なッ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一応書いてみたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:24.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}東洋の定型詩なんだけど　どうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:29.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君を待つ　岸壁に吹く　風寒し
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:33.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}短いわね　歌詞に使えるかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}次俺　　俺の番
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ほら　傑作だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.30,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここは地獄さ　ノーホープ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お前がいなきゃ　ノーフューチャー
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.81,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}って　何よこれ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}俺の魂シャウトだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}響くだろ　ハートに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何だよ　文句あんのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大体　お前らが書いたのだって…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これも頂きます
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かってんじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:02.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:03.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:07.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}皆さん　たくさんの歌詞をありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:11.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　本当にそれでいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たくさんの武器を頂きました
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アルド
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.23,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう　諦めるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:46.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かってるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.62,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}けど　こだわってるのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたも同じでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すごい数だな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これ全部　君が書いたのかい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.55,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}郵便社の人たちが手伝ってくれました
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ふ～む　今見た感じだと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多分イルマはオッケーしないと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:15.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これは君に依頼した仕事ではなかったかな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが私はドールです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私の業務は歌詞を書くことではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ちょっと　付き合ってもらえるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違うわ！もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今のはもっとゆっくり歌いたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:43.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なるべく静かに　けれど確かにそこにある感じで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:45.34,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}服装が…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}違うだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい　普通すぎます
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.39,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今の時代の誰もが着ている服のままです
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}オペラというのは　もっと古い時代のものではないでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古典といいますか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.61,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あれは練習用の服ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:09.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いや　あれが次の舞台の衣装だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イルマが言いだしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「次の作品は新作にしたい」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:19.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「もっと今の人たちに伝わる舞台にしたい」ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:23.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦争が終わって　平和な時代が来たはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.82,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本当にみんなが幸せっているのかしら？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}新しい時代を開くのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私たち一人一人が！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:37.20,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あの戦争は多くの人々に傷痕を残した
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:41.47,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今もその人々の心は凍りついたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}次の時代の到来を感じることも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前に進みだすこともできていないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:53.49,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この物語は彼女に頼まれて私が書いた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.02,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヒロインのモデルはイルマ自身だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曲も私が全部作って
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼女と相談しながら進めていたんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:06.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私もイルマもクライマックスで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:11.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヒロインが恋人に書いた手紙を読み上げるシーンの歌詞が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:12.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:16.84,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}どうしても納得のいくものにならなかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:23.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恋文ならドールにお願いするのはどうだろうという話になってね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:27.53,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知り合いの郵便協会の人にアドバイスしてもらったら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君の名前が出たんだ　確か…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.58,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ローダンセという人だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:37.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたが良きドールになりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ローダンセ教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:45.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}教官が私を推薦してくださったのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:49.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ　イルマが作りたい歌の内容を伝えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼女が君の名前を教えてくれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:57.75,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「とても難しい依頼ですが　できそうなドールが1人います」と
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:04.83,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「彼女なら　今を生きる人々に届く恋文を書けるかもしれません」とね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:08.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もう少し　手伝ってくれないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}それじゃあお先ね　お疲れ様
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ　お疲れ様
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.06,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何でついてくるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.88,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イルマさんの心をしりたいのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はあ？　何言ってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}良きドールとは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人の言葉の中から
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:41.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伝えたい本当の心をすくい上げるものなのです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.94,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だから私についてくるっていうの
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:45.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.40,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}任務遂行上　必要なのです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなた疲れを知らないの
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:10.87,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行軍訓練では　完全装備で２０メリド以上を歩いたこともあります
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなた…軍にいたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:17.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたは帰ってこられたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.85,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたにも　大切な人がいるでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何よりね　大切な人と再会できて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:44.41,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたが帰ってきて喜んでるでしょ…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その人も
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.99,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かりません
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:52.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その方は私の上官で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:56.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後の戦いのさなか行方が分からなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:01.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私はその方が今　どこでどうされているのか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知らされておりません
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.48,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ついて来て　いいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:15.64,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}こっちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:28.32,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここが初めて彼と　フーゴと歩いた場所よ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:33.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦争に行って帰らない人ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そう　私の恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アルドの息子なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}アルドさんの…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:44.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ええ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:50.96,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}戦争に行く当日も　フーゴと2人で　ここに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:14.72,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必ず…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.01,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必ず帰ってこい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}…帰ってくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必ず…帰ってくるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:49.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私　アルドにもひどいこと行っちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:52.57,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}彼だってつらいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私だって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:59.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もうフーゴが帰ってこないことくらい分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:02.54,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そんな簡単に…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:10.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}諦められるわけないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:17.04,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなた！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:20.63,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:25.05,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}よかった　無事で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:33.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}じゃあ　ここで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:35.51,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}イルマさん
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:39.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私　少しイルマさんの心に近づけた気がします
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:41.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:43.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歌詞が書けるかどうかは…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:52.27,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もっと私の心が知りたいなら　手紙を見せてあげてもいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:55.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が彼宛てに書いた手紙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.74,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全部宛先不明で返ってきたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:03.00,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だけど　それを見ても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:06.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私の心をすくい上げたものにしかならない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.71,0:23:11.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私の欲しい歌は　そういうのじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.47,0:23:14.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべての女性が共感し
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:17.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}すべての男性の胸を打つ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:19.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですか…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:25.19,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット　付き合ってくれてありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:30.24,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}1人じゃないのも悪くなかったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:56.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:00.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ローランドさん
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:03.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ベネディクトから聞いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:07.14,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あんた難しい仕事を受けてるんだってな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:09.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}はい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:11.50,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.77,0:24:15.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私は…愛を知らないのに
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.68,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛を言葉にできるのでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:26.42,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今日仕事終わったら少し時間をもらえるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.88,0:24:33.98,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}わしには難しいことはよく分からんが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.66,0:24:38.33,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}手紙はな　宛先があればそこに届く
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.86,0:24:42.52,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}なければ送り主に戻されることになってるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.17,0:24:44.13,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分かるかい
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:48.92,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}存じています　私も郵便社の所属ですので
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:54.46,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}でも　戦争は残酷で　相手を選ばないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.53,0:24:59.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}着いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.20,0:25:06.15,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここは…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.47,0:25:10.28,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}軍の管轄だった郵便局の倉庫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.19,0:25:13.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今はもう使われてない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:19.60,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この手紙は？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.35,0:25:21.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その手紙だけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.95,0:25:24.26,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここにある手紙は
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.57,0:25:27.80,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}行く先も　送り主も失った手紙たちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.45,0:25:53.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛…してる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.80,0:25:56.91,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛しています…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:25:59.25,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}あなたを愛してる…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.56,0:26:00.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛しいあなた…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.16,0:26:02.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛を君に…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.85,0:26:04.08,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛する妻より
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.76,0:26:08.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}愛はいつも　私の心に
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:14.77,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}この手紙すべてに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.33,0:26:18.07,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}書いた人の心が込められているのに
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.72,0:26:21.66,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}その想いは誰にも伝わることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.89,0:26:26.67,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}航空祭があれば　空からまいてあげられるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.92,0:26:28.79,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}皆さん…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.81,0:26:33.59,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ご自分の「愛してる」を手紙にこめているのですね
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.58,0:26:38.10,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ああ　そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.92,0:26:47.95,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私が彼宛てに書いた手紙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.44,0:26:52.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全部　宛先不明で返ってきたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.86,0:27:01.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}実はね　私の両親　死んじゃったの
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.01,0:27:06.70,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}お父さんも　お母さんも　遺品すら見つからなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.54,0:27:09.76,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心から…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.90,0:27:35.38,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}改めて書き直しました
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.67,0:27:40.86,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ですが　やはりこういうのではなかったでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.18,0:27:49.09,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}もしかして　イルマさんの心をすくい上げただけになってしまっているでしょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.14,0:27:55.69,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そうかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.98,0:28:00.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}けれど
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.84,0:28:06.21,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これは　私が欲しかったものよ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.83,0:28:07.71,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.52,0:28:12.22,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}うん
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.18,0:28:16.16,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}いい歌詞だ　驚いたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.90,0:28:19.90,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失礼な話だが　初めて会った時
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.40,0:28:23.97,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君にこんな歌詞が書けるとは思わなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.88,0:28:28.37,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私も…そう思っておりました
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.03,0:28:32.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレット
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.36,0:28:43.43,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.46,0:31:29.65,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ヴァイオレットの書いた手紙が
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.21,0:31:34.93,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凍っていた私のイルマの時間を動かし始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.53,0:31:39.11,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここにいる私たちは　この歌と共に
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.37,0:31:42.35,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ここから新しい時を刻み始める
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:28.56,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}そして
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.54,0:32:33.18,VIOLET-text-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}君にもいつか
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.86,0:01:27.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她给我的第一印象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}宛如一个人偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:32.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}实在无法想象她能够
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:36.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写出伊尔玛所要求的书信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:23.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}伊尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:25.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}辛苦了 奥尔多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:29.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想给你介绍一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:32.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.59,0:03:36.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要客人有要求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.66,0:03:39.96,VIOLET-text,,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不论身在何处 都能为您服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我是自动手记人偶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特·伊芙加登
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你就是传言所说的人偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:49.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}传言？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:55.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}邮政协会的老师还专门向我推荐你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:57.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请问您说的是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:02.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}伊尔玛小姐 这是布雷迪伯爵送来的花束和书信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:05.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是缪特将军送来的花束和照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:08.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想跟您谈谈接下来关于采访的事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}奥尔多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:13.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}告诉她 麻烦明天来我家一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:15.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.68,0:04:19.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}伊尔玛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:22.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}等下有时间和我谈谈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:25.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}又要讲那件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:26.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}昨天真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}来 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呐 话说你昨天听我唱歌了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的 虽然我还是第一次听歌剧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:46.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但那真是让人全身都为之震撼的歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:48.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:49.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为歌词是古典语言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有一部分还是没有听懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请问这首歌的内容到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:02.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:06.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.36,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开始工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么 我先询问一些必要信息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:15.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}首先是收信人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:19.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}寄信人写伊尔玛·费利斯 这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是写我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}麻烦写玛丽埃塔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:26.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是假名吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么可能 不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后对方则是她的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.29,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}名字叫莫德斯托
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他去了战场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还…没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}莫德斯托先生对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}然后请问他的姓氏 还有住址在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.15,0:05:51.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那些根本无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}毕竟重要的是内容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:59.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么就让我们开始写正文
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:01.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:03.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是说要开始写正文吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:22.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以我要你自己想一想 然后写出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}思念着还没从战争中回来的莫德斯托
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}深爱着他的玛丽埃塔会写下的情书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:29.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}自动手记人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:34.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写出这封信 不就是你的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:38.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:52.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:54.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}读来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:00.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}亲爱的莫德斯托先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:04.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}玛丽埃塔当前在战斗区域以外待机中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我无法确认莫德斯托先生是否平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:13.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}请您尽快下达指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}玛丽埃塔敬上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:21.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是…什么…像是军人写的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为小姐您让我自己想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}您不满意这封信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要听到这些话语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所有女性都会为之共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.13,0:07:41.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所有男性都会为之触动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:43.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想要这样的情书
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}共鸣…触动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}再写一遍试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:05.89,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}雨果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:20.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}想必我将会永远爱慕着你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算灵魂坠入地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:27.12,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}记忆中残存的你那甘美醉人的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.16,0:08:28.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}依然使我不住震颤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:33.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我挣扎着将那快要消逝的思念再次牵系起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:39.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是什么时代的情书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:40.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太陈腐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:44.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我要的是现代的 有情节的情书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}情节
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:10.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我深深地 深深地爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:12.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好爱你 好爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好爱你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:18.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样写的话 现在的任何人读到都会吓跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}写的时候多考虑一下时代感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:25.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}时代…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:53.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:58.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你在做什么 薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:06.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你正在为歌剧院的女歌手代写情书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:11.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果有什么好玩的八卦 悄悄告诉我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:21.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没问题吧 遇到什么困难了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:22.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}客人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:26.03,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}客人委托的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太有难度了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:34.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我还是第一次听你发牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:37.17,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这封情书有这么难写吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:41.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她说要写出所有女性都会为之共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所有男性都会为之触动的情书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:46.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:48.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}确实很不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你们两位写得出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:26.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}辛苦了 薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:29.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}奥尔多先生 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}听说这份委托 你做得不太顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:37.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的 无论怎么写都无法让她满意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.61,0:11:42.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}毕竟伊尔玛也全身心投入到这次歌剧的新作品上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:44.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}新作品？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:47.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这和我写的信有什么关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 委托你写的不是信而是歌词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:54.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是写给这次歌剧高潮部分的咏叹调的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:57.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你看 就是这首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:02.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么 工作不是代笔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而是写歌词吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}据奥尔多大人所说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:09.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原本一开始就是这样的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:11.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:14.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}商讨委托内容的时候没注意到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}因为是邮政协会那边委托过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我还以为肯定就是代写书信了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:25.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这里是女主角读出自己写下的情书的场景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:29.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}原来如此 写情书这一点并没有弄错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:32.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那么 你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.59,0:12:36.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然这是我已经受理的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:38.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但和我的业务范围并不一致
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.85,0:12:42.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这点事不是很简单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:43.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:46.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算不是代写书信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:48.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}只要我们写出最棒的歌词不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:51.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我说你啊 这事没那么简单哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:56.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们这里可是聚集了这么多优秀的人偶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:57.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.78,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且 填个词什么的就算让我来也成…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你这人真是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:09.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你真的能写出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不试试怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}姑且试着写了一首
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.04,0:13:24.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是东洋的格律诗 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:29.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不辞万苦待君归 岸壁之上不胜寒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:33.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好短呢 能当歌词用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.26,0:13:34.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}下一个是我 轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}看看 这可是杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:41.30,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}此处是地狱 No hope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:44.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如果没有你 No future
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.81,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这写的什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:48.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是我灵魂的shout啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.07,0:13:50.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}震撼你的heart了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么啊 有意见么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:56.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}而且 你们写的不也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这个我也收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你很懂嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:02.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:03.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.02,0:14:07.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢大家 帮我写出这么多的歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:11.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 这些真的行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我从大家手中收到了很多武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:35.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}奥尔多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:40.23,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}差不多 该放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:46.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我懂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.62,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是 你不也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没放下心结吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:01.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:04.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这些全都是你写的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.55,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}邮政公司的同事们给予了我帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 在我看来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}估计这些也不会让伊尔玛满意的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:15.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}况且
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:19.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是委托给你个人的工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:23.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但我是一名人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:26.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的业务并不是写歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.93,0:15:32.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能耽误你一会儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不对！ 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.25,0:15:39.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}刚才的歌要唱得更缓慢一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:43.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要尽量轻柔 但要清晰地表现出在场感
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.53,0:15:45.34,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他们的服装…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.08,0:15:48.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不一样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.79,0:15:50.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的 太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:54.39,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都是现在这个时代人们会穿的服装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:59.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所谓歌剧 不是更传统的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}该称作古典什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.61,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那是练习时穿的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:09.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不 那是下一次舞台上用的戏服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是伊尔玛提出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「下一场想演新作品」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:19.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}说是想表现得更贴近现在的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:23.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明明战争已经结束 我们迎来了和平的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.82,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但大家真的感到幸福了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.95,0:16:29.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我们要用自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:32.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开启崭新的时代！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.57,0:16:37.20,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那场战争给许多人造成无法磨灭的伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.12,0:16:41.47,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}人们依旧冰封着自己的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:44.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既无法感受新时代的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也无法迈出前进的脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:53.49,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这个故事是她拜托我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.02,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}女主角的原型就是伊尔玛自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}曲子也全都是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和她商量着创作出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:06.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我和伊尔玛都对高潮部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:11.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}女主角读出写给恋人的信这一场景 所唱的歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.67,0:17:12.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对那首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:16.84,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么也不能满意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这时候她说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:23.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}既然是写情书 不如拜托人偶来写如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:27.53,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她向邮政协会的熟人咨询了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那个人就说出你的名字 我记得…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.58,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她名字叫罗丹丝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:37.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}希望你能成为一名优秀的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.36,0:17:40.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}罗丹丝教官…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:45.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是教官推荐我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:49.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是啊 我把伊尔玛想写的歌曲内容告诉她以后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她就把你的名字告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:57.75,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}她说「虽然这项委托很困难 但有一个人偶或许做得到」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:04.83,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}「她的话 也许能够写出传达给时下世人的情书」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:08.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能请你 再帮帮忙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那我先走了 辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 您也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.06,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你为什么要跟着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:31.88,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想理解伊尔玛小姐的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}什么？ 你说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:35.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}优秀的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能够从人们的话语中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:41.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}提取出对方真正想要表达的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:44.94,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所以你要跟着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:45.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.40,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}为了完成任务 这是必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你就不知道累的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:10.87,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}行军训练的时候 全副武装行进20梅里多以上也是常事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你…在军队里待过？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:17.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你还是回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:32.85,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你也有珍重的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:40.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}和珍重的人重逢 一定是比什么都重要的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:44.41,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你能回来他也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:48.99,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:52.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他是我的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:56.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在最后的战役中 下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:01.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现在他身在何处 是否平安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有人告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.48,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你可以跟着我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:15.64,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:28.32,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是我和他 跟雨果第一次散步的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:33.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是那个奔赴战场没能回来的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对 他是我的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:39.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也是阿尔多的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:43.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}阿尔多先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:44.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.25,0:20:50.96,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他去战场的那一天 我们两个人又来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:14.72,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.01,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}一定要给我回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:25.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}…会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:32.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我一定…会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:49.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我 对阿尔多也说了过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.07,0:21:52.57,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}他一定也很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:56.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}就算是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:21:59.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也知道雨果再也回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.62,0:22:02.54,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:07.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:10.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这么容易就放弃希望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.26,0:22:17.04,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}亲爱的！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:20.63,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.81,0:22:25.05,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}太好了 你平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:33.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那就在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:35.51,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}伊尔玛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.06,0:22:39.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我感觉自己稍稍接近了伊尔玛小姐的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.81,0:22:41.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:43.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}还不知道能不能写出歌词…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:52.27,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要是想更深了解我的话 可以给你看我写的信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.30,0:22:55.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我写给他的信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:22:58.74,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然全都因为收信人地址不明退了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:03.00,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过 就算你看了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.03,0:23:06.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}也最多不过了解我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.71,0:23:11.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我想要的歌曲 不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.47,0:23:14.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要让所有女性都会为之共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:17.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所有男性都会为之触动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.42,0:23:19.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.84,0:23:25.19,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特 谢谢你陪我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:30.24,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}有人一起也不是坏事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:56.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:00.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}罗兰德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:03.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我听贝内迪克特说了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.03,0:24:07.14,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}说是你接手了一个很困难的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:09.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.77,0:24:11.50,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.77,0:24:15.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…明明连爱都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.71,0:24:18.68,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}能用语言表达出爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:26.42,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}今天工作结束后可以占用你一点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.88,0:24:33.98,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我虽然不懂那些复杂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.66,0:24:38.33,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对我来说 有收信人的信就投递给收信人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.86,0:24:42.52,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有的话就退给写信人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.17,0:24:44.13,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}你懂么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.98,0:24:48.92,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我知道的 毕竟我也是邮递公司的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:54.46,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是战争是残酷的 子弹是不长眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.53,0:24:59.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}到了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.20,0:25:06.15,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.47,0:25:10.28,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这是过去军属邮局的仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.19,0:25:13.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}现在已经没在使用了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:19.60,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这封信是？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.35,0:25:21.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不只是这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.95,0:25:24.26,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这里所有的信
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.57,0:25:27.80,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都是既找不到收信人也找不到写信人的信
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.45,0:25:53.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我…爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.80,0:25:56.91,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我爱你…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.75,0:25:59.25,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我爱你…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.56,0:26:00.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}亲爱的…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.16,0:26:02.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我的爱属于你…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.85,0:26:04.08,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爱你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.76,0:26:08.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}对你的爱永存我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:14.77,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}所有的这些信
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.33,0:26:18.07,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都饱含着写信人的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.72,0:26:21.66,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但这些感情 却没有传达给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.89,0:26:26.67,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}要是有航空节的话 倒是可以把它们抛洒到空中的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.92,0:26:28.79,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.81,0:26:33.59,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}都把自己的「我爱你」倾注在了字里行间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.58,0:26:38.10,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.92,0:26:47.95,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我写给他的信
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.44,0:26:52.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然全部因为收信人地址不明退回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.86,0:27:01.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}其实啊 我的双亲都去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.01,0:27:06.70,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}爸爸妈妈连遗物都没能留下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.54,0:27:09.76,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我真心地…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.90,0:27:35.38,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我又重新写了一份
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.67,0:27:40.86,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不过 果然您要求的不是这样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.18,0:27:49.09,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}或许 我只是发现了伊尔玛小姐的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.14,0:27:55.69,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.98,0:28:00.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.84,0:28:06.21,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}这就是 我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.83,0:28:07.71,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.52,0:28:12.22,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.18,0:28:16.16,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}真是好歌词 真让我吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.90,0:28:19.90,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}虽然说来失礼 第一次见到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.40,0:28:23.97,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}没有想到你能写出这样的歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.88,0:28:28.37,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我当时…也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.03,0:28:32.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.36,0:28:43.43,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.46,0:31:29.65,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}薇尔莉特写的这封信
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.21,0:31:34.93,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}让我和伊尔玛心中冻结的时间再次开始转动
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.53,0:31:39.11,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}在这里 我们和这歌声一起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.37,0:31:42.35,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}向新的未来迈步
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:28.56,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}我相信
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.54,0:32:33.18,VIOLET-text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}总有一天你也会
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.41,0:32:43.93,VIOLET_3,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(965.333,678.333)}「总有一天你也会知晓“爱”的意义」
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——OP——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.61,0:01:45.21,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}知らない言葉を　覚えてゆくたび
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:51.71,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}おもかげのなか　手を伸ばすの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:58.31,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}だけど一人では　分からない言葉も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.73,0:02:01.82,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}あるのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.13,0:02:06.41,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}さよならは　苦くて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:13.47,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}アイシテルは　遠いにおいがした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:21.56,VIOLET_opjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}例えようのない　この思いは
